    <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--ash);max-width:680px;line-height:1.75">Every Indian personal finance platform shows you a list and lets you figure it out. BankBazaar, Paisabazaar — they are directories. Global leaders like NerdWallet, MoneySavingExpert, ClearScore show you what to do, and why. InvestingPro is built from that philosophy: every design decision, every copy line, every interaction should feel like advice from a brilliant, honest friend who happens to know finance deeply.</p>
    <div class="phil-cols">
