<!-- ══════════════ COPYWRITING ══════════════ -->
<div class="doc-section" id="s-copy">
  <div class="copy-section">
    <div class="ds-title">Copywriting <em>Voice</em></div>
    <div class="ds-sub">Every word on InvestingPro is a trust decision. The voice is: direct, honest, slightly warm, never promotional, always specific. This is the single most differentiated element — no Indian competitor writes this well.</div>

    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr;gap:24px;margin-bottom:36px">
      <div class="voice-card">
        <h3>The InvestingPro Voice</h3>
        <div class="voice-example">"The HDFC Infinia is everyone's dream card — and we'll be honest about why most people shouldn't apply for it yet."</div>
        <div class="voice-example">"We earn commission when you apply. That's how we stay free for you. It never changes what we recommend."</div>
        <div class="voice-example">"Your CIBIL of 748 gives you an 82% approval chance for this card. Apply with confidence."</div>
        <ul class="voice-rules">
          <li>Direct and specific. "82% approval chance" not "good chance."</li>
          <li>Include the honest downside on every recommendation.</li>
          <li>Use "you" and "your" — never "users" or "customers."</li>
          <li>Use Indian context: ₹, "crore", "lakh", "EMI", "SIP."</li>
          <li>Never say "best in class" or "world-class." Be specific.</li>
          <li>Acknowledge commission openly. It builds not destroys trust.</li>
          <li>Sentences under 20 words whenever possible.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px">
        <div style="background:var(--paper);border-radius:var(--r12);padding:20px;border:1.5px solid var(--mist)">
          <div style="font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:8.5px;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ash);margin-bottom:10px">Tone Spectrum</div>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px">
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:12px"><span style="color:var(--green)">✓</span><strong>Honest</strong> — always</div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:12px"><span style="color:var(--green)">✓</span><strong>Specific</strong> — numbers always</div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:12px"><span style="color:var(--green)">✓</span><strong>Warm</strong> — not cold</div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:12px"><span style="color:var(--red)">✗</span>Promotional</div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:12px"><span style="color:var(--red)">✗</span>Jargon-heavy</div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:12px"><span style="color:var(--red)">✗</span>Vague superlatives</div>
