          <div style="font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:8.5px;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--saffron);margin-bottom:10px">Editorial Independence</div>
          <div style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:15px;font-style:italic;color:var(--cream);line-height:1.5">"Our rankings are based on objective criteria. Commission never changes them."</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:rgba(245,240,232,.4);margin-top:8px">— This one line, placed above every list, is InvestingPro's most powerful copy.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="phil-label">Bad copy → Good copy transformations</div>
    <div class="copy-grid">
      <div class="copy-card">
        <h3>🏠 Hero Headline</h3>
        <div class="copy-bad">"India's Best Financial Products Comparison Platform. Compare Credit Cards, Loans, Mutual Funds and More!"</div>
        <div class="copy-good">"India's most trusted financial advisor.<br>We compare 500+ products so you don't have to."</div>
        <p class="copy-why">The bad version says what you do. The good version says what you are. "Trusted advisor" is the position, not "comparison platform."</p>
      </div>
      <div class="copy-card">
        <h3>💳 Card Recommendation</h3>
        <div class="copy-bad">"The SBI Cashback Credit Card offers amazing 5% cashback on all online purchases! Apply now for exclusive offers!"</div>
        <div class="copy-good">"5% cashback on every online spend — no merchant restrictions. The best straightforward cashback card for most Indians. The catch: no lounge access and a ₹1,000 annual fee from Year 2."</div>
        <p class="copy-why">The good version is specific, includes a downside, and trusts the reader with reality. That honesty makes the recommendation 4x more credible.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="copy-card">
        <h3>🏦 Loan Page Intro</h3>
        <div class="copy-bad">"Looking for the best home loan? Compare home loan interest rates from top banks in India and find the lowest EMI!"</div>
        <div class="copy-good">"Home loan rates just fell to an 8-year low. Before you apply, here's what your CIBIL score and income actually determine — and why the 'lowest rate' headline is often misleading."</div>
        <p class="copy-why">Timely context, honest warning, specific claim. Builds trust while setting up the comparison table as a genuinely useful tool.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="copy-card">
        <h3>📊 CIBIL Tool</h3>
        <div class="copy-bad">"Check your CIBIL score for free! Improve your credit score with our tips and tricks!"</div>
        <div class="copy-good">"Your CIBIL score determines your home loan rate. A score of 750+ could save you ₹3.2 lakh over 20 years. See yours free — and we'll show you exactly what's pulling it down."</div>
        <p class="copy-why">Specific ₹ impact first. Then the offer. The value is stated before the ask. Always lead with the "so what" not the feature.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="copy-card">
        <h3>✉️ Email CTA</h3>
        <div class="copy-bad">"Subscribe to our newsletter for latest financial news and updates!"</div>
        <div class="copy-good">"InvestingPro Weekly. Every Monday: rate changes that affect your EMI, new cards worth knowing about, and one tax tip. 60 seconds. Free forever."</div>
        <p class="copy-why">Tell them exactly what they get, how long it takes, and how often. Every word earns its place. "60 seconds" makes it feel safe to commit.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="copy-card">
        <h3>🤝 Trust / Commission</h3>
        <div class="copy-bad">"Disclaimer: InvestingPro may earn referral fees. This does not affect our recommendations."</div>
        <div class="copy-good">"We earn commission when you apply through us. That's how we stay free. We never rank a card higher because of what it pays us — here's our exact methodology."</div>
        <p class="copy-why">The "disclaimer" buries trust. The good version leads with it. Radical transparency about commission is the most counterintuitive and effective trust signal.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="phil-label">Headline Gallery — Across Contexts</div>
    <div class="headline-gallery">
